      <item>
        <title>How to use RequireJS with Rails</title>
        <description>&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Hello there,&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Well, it’s september and I didn’t post nothing since July. :/ Let’s do this!&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;h2 id=&quot;requirejs--rails&quot;&gt;RequireJS + Rails&lt;/h2&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;So, a few days ago I was playing with a Rails project and I started to think how to implement &lt;a href=&quot;http://requirejs.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;RequireJS&lt;/a&gt; with Rails. For those who don’t know what the heck it’s RequireJS, here’s a little overview from his website:&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;blockquote&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;RequireJS is a JavaScript file and module loader. It is optimized for in-browser use, but it can be used in other JavaScript environments, like Rhino and Node. Using a modular script loader like RequireJS will improve the speed and quality of your code.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/blockquote&gt;

  &lt;h2 id=&quot;the-requirejs-rails-gem&quot;&gt;The requirejs-rails Gem&lt;/h2&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Fortunately, there’s a Gem that makes ease to implement RequireJS in a Rails project, check out &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jwhitley/requirejs-rails&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;h2 id=&quot;using-requirejs-rails-gem&quot;&gt;Using requirejs-rails Gem&lt;/h2&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;You’ll need to install the Gem, so add it in your Gemfile:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;gem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;requirejs-rails&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Run &lt;code&gt;bundle update&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;bundle install&lt;/code&gt; and we’ll be ready to go!&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Next step, create a &lt;code&gt;requirejs.yml&lt;/code&gt; file in the &lt;code&gt;config&lt;/code&gt; folder. This file will be our configuration file, where we can put our paths and shim. Take a look in the example bellow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-yaml&quot; data-lang=&quot;yaml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;paths&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# File paths and names&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;delta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;delta&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;application&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;application&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;jquery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;jquery&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;jquery_ujs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;jquery_ujs&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;turbolinks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;turbolinks&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;shim&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# http://requirejs.org/docs/api.html#config-shim&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;jquery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;exports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;jquery&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;jquery_ujs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;deps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;jquery&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# Default app name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;modules&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;l-Scalar-Plain&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p-Indicator&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;application&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Now it’s time to remove all Sprockets directives, like &lt;code&gt;//= require jquery&lt;/code&gt; from your js files.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;You can write your scripts using the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/amdjs/amdjs-api/blob/master/AMD.md&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Asynchronous Module Definition (AMD)&lt;/a&gt; like so:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot; data-lang=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// delta.js file&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;define&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;([&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;jquery&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;jquery_ujs&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;turbolinks&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;],&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;use strict&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;delta&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{};&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;delta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;init&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;addLoader&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;p&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;removeLoader&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;delta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;addLoader&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;delta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;removeLoader&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;delta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;init&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;();&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;});&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Calling &lt;code&gt;delta.js&lt;/code&gt; file in your &lt;code&gt;application.js&lt;/code&gt; file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-javascript&quot; data-lang=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// application.js file&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nx&quot;&gt;require&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;([&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;delta&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;],&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;});&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Doing that, just run &lt;code&gt;rake assets:precompile&lt;/code&gt; and we’re done!&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;h2 id=&quot;odd-thing&quot;&gt;Odd thing&lt;/h2&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;If you’re using &lt;a href=&quot;https://rails-assets.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Rails Assets&lt;/a&gt;, there’s a bug with the last version of requirejs-rails Gem, I found this but don’t know how to fix yet, the only solution for me was to downgrade the Gem to &lt;code&gt;0.9.3&lt;/code&gt; version. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jwhitley/requirejs-rails/issues/188&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Here’s the issue&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;h2 id=&quot;wrapping-up&quot;&gt;Wrapping up&lt;/h2&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;RequireJS is a great solution to write modularized and decoupled JavaScript, but sometimes it can be unnecessary. I recommend you to take a look and test it, not only RequireJS, but &lt;a href=&quot;http://browserify.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Browserify&lt;/a&gt; also, after all, we are not forced to use these solution.&lt;/p&gt;

  &lt;p&gt;Cya!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
